# Typography Standards

## For New Components (USE THESE)

### Headings
- Hero/Page Title: `className="heading-1"`
- Section Headings: `className="heading-2"`
- Sub-sections: `className="heading-3"`
- Small headings: `className="heading-4"`

### Body Text
- Standard: `className="body-text"`
- Large/readable: `className="body-large"`

### UI Elements
- Buttons/Nav: `text-ui font-ui`
- Small labels: `text-ui-xs font-ui`

## Migration (Optional, Do Gradually)

When editing existing components:
- Replace `text-4xl md:text-6xl` → `heading-1`
- Replace `text-2xl md:text-4xl` → `heading-2`
- Only change when you're already editing that file
